### URL DECODE
URL-decodes the input, or returns `null` and adds a warning header to the response if the input cannot be decoded.

```esql
ROW u = "https%3A%2F%2Fexample.com%2F%3Fx%3Dfoo%20bar%26y%3Dbaz"
| EVAL u = URL_DECODE(u)
```
